Hi Harris,

You can only have an angle _between_ two things.  Do you mean the
angle between the line segment and the x-axis?  To find that angle,
you'd use trigonometry:

  Trigonometry in a Nutshell
  http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/53942.html

Does this help? 

